  "description": "Philippine Financial Access MCP Server. 587 BSP-supervised institutions across 7 categories (universal, thrift, rural, cooperative, digital banks, quasi-banks, non-bank FIs), 37,834 geocoded branch and ATM locations, and financial inclusion analytics. Built on Cloudflare Workers.",
  "author": "Aaron Zara <aaron.zara@godmode.ph>",
